STEER: FULLY OPEN / HIGHEST-EV. Do NOT constrain to nonprofit or civic. Find the single highest-scoring idea against the rubric + prohibited list from the ENTIRE space. Consider all the thought-starters Anthropic listed: ship a product somewhere new (mobile/desktop/CLI); a claims/loan-servicing/back-office workflow that takes weeks today, collapsed to minutes; a long-overdue redesign; "the swarm" — point a team of agents at a real backlog and ship the release. Also consider dev-tools, agentic infra, B2B workflow automation, creative/generative tools, and anything that showcases Opus 4.8 + orchestration in a way that surprises Anthropic judges. Pick whatever scores highest, NOT whatever is most socially worthy.
PROHIBITED (instant DQ): AI Mental Health Advisor; Basic RAG apps; Streamlit apps; Image Analyzers; "AI for Education" chatbot; AI Job Application Screener; AI Nutrition Coach; Personality Analyzers; Medical advice bots; ANY project where a dashboard is the main feature; Sports analyzers/coaches; anything using code/data/assets without rights.
